entry.title: Grevillea rosmarinifolia hybrids
entry.content: A natural hybrid between Grevillea rosmarinifolia and G. chrysophaea. Habit similar to G. rosmarinifolia from this area, being low shrub. Only a few plants observed here. More common hybrid form here of these two species is taller, open shrub similar in form to G. chrysophaea.
